{"tid":2040692,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] PES MOBILE 2020討論帖（214）熱烈come啤","createTime":"2020-05-28T17:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T18:05:15.000Z","uid":48573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b083bf3079ec0920bba0cc2cab9b58a038c0ec23","tid":2040692,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:59:22.000Z","msg":"● 官網：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.konami.com/wepes/mobile/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.konami.com%2Fwepes%2Fmobile%2Fen%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=e64e57a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.konami.com/wepes/mobile/en/</a><br />\n● Download Link<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/pes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer/id1117270703?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fpes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer%2Fid1117270703%3Fmt%3D8&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=3c6a82ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/pes-2018-pro-evolution-soccer/id1117270703?mt=8</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.konami.pesam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Djp.konami.pesam&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=7e4897e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.konami.pesam</a><br />\n<br />\n● 新手開波Q&amp;A?<br />\n<br />\n1. 洗唔洗刷首抽?<br />\n新手開波既時候會有好多抽，盡量黑波起手，coins留黎抽Fp(精選球員)，唔滿意既可以繼續刷到自己想要既球員為止。<br />\n<br />\n3. 點樣改Email或者密碼?<br />\n<a href=\"https://my.konami.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.konami.net%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=f5ea7e53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://my.konami.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 操控方法<br />\n操控類型有 Advanced 同 Classic 揀<br />\n推薦 Classic 佢類似手制咁樣同埋易上手啲<br />\n<br />\n● 球員資料<br />\nPES DATABASE<br />\n<a href=\"http://pesdb.net/pes2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpesdb.net%2Fpes2020%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=e478bbc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pesdb.net/pes2020/</a><br />\n要注意由於可能有球員更新，所以DATABASE 入面既100%抽球員可能有誤。<br />\n<br />\n只需要直接search球員名，你就可以搵到該球員特性同數值。<br />\n而想搵一堆某類球員，可以憑Search Conditions自行set Filters 搵出黎。<br />\n<br />\n● 不同底色球員資料<br />\n紅色=強化版legend(非常難中)(使用該球會球衣有加乘)<br />\n金色=普通版legend<br />\n<br />\n紫色=強化版現役(現實比賽中表現良好的球員會出現係fp pool到)<br />\n藍色=普通版現役(可以3個黑波換一個)<br />\n灰色=舊版現役(2019版本或之前)<br />\n<br />\n●畫面調整<br />\n新手入game 第一件事畫質轉60fps<br />\n<br />\n但30fps low quality 比較慳電<br />\n<br />\n教練，球員，沒有最強只有更強<br />\n因該每次更新，Konami 都會暗改教練球員走位，唔會通知，要靠老手用過先知<br />\n<br />\n●實時系統<br />\n每周四維護6小時（10am-4pm)後，會按照現實球員表現而調整球員狀態；<br />\n另有巴打 隨時更新球員實際操作表現（暗改），詳情要留意留言<br />\n<br />\n●教練更新<br />\n即日起，可簽入不同版本的同名教練。每日更新3次，已擁有的教練不能再簽下<br />\n<br />\n●拍賣<br />\n根本球員條件（國籍，球會，年歲，能力）買球探組合球員<br />\n詳情：PES DATABASE<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://pesdb.net/pes2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpesdb.net%2Fpes2020%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=e478bbc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pesdb.net/pes2020/</a><br />\n<br />\n●賺取Gp方法<br />\n<br />\nOpen challenge ，打哂三關有75000gp<br />\n<br />\nMatchday ，除左部分比賽有coins外，每關夠1500積分，可以觀戰賺取gp<br />\n<br />\n季節賽掛tour(適宜新手)，以白銅銀波掛機，升班可以賺取23000~24000gp<br />\n<br />\n●遊戲玩法<br />\n<br />\nTour &amp;Tour Sim<br />\n用fp球員既%會高d (分數較高)<br />\n<br />\n最少打2500 points 賺導師(幫球員升lv)<br />\n<br />\ncampaign sim <br />\n<br />\n刷gp 用狀態A/B 銀波+白波bench(升班有23000gp~24000gp)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n●Matchday<br />\n<br />\nPreset team<br />\n有coins既matchday 就打夠5500分<br />\n想刷gp可以繼續打 前300名可以參加比賽(抽籤)<br />\n無coins既matchday 打1500分就得 記得觀戰賺gp<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自已球員代表球會出戰<br />\n<br />\n係度search自已個名 查到所代表球會及你打既積分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://efootballpro.konami.net/open/rankings/season-program/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fefootballpro.konami.net%2Fopen%2Frankings%2Fseason-program%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=94bcdfbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://efootballpro.konami.net/open/rankings/season-program/</a><br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n521～611 Iconic moment <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歷年連登杯冠軍名單<br />\n<br />\n2020UEFA:月城雪兔<br />\n2020World cup:出奧燒啦<br />\n2020歐洲x南美杯:出奧燒啦<br />\n2500戰力杯:Aristo<br />\n<br />\n第二屆普黑團體盃賽: Aristo 一生人三次<br />\nwaiiiiiiii 我朋友係金毛獅王<br />\n<br />\nPes mobile三巨頭<br />\n牛<br />\n兔<br />\n啤"},{"pid":"a3838fd776c05c74cdaa954ebe7ed5dab0ac255d","tid":2040692,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"我屌,copy唔到圖的？"},{"pid":"1d72b3628079cd0a13b3cf2e0af53132d753d202","tid":2040692,"uid":135206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T18:02:17.000Z","msg":"any"},{"pid":"07d1910b273e5bdb8780ea736d558f25ff76828e","tid":2040692,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3838fd776c05c74cdaa954ebe7ed5dab0ac255d","tid":2040692,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"我屌,copy唔到圖的？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T18:02:28.000Z","msg":"要用個post右上個個function, 你開過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26709fd4b6a58a50811c5160201c48dfee289e7","tid":2040692,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T18:05:12.000Z","msg":"啤 太多話我想說<br />\n但我 還是要啞口道別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eebbc296370966e31340541b2cdf83559d1a1a1","tid":2040692,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07d1910b273e5bdb8780ea736d558f25ff76828e","tid":2040692,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3838fd776c05c74cdaa954ebe7ed5dab0ac255d","tid":2040692,"uid":48573,